casebody.data:
[41 C.2d 901;

256 P.2d 933] [L. A. No. 21698. In Bank. May 12, 1953.] HOYT REED, Appellant, v. CARL O. NORMAN et al., Respondents. Hy Schwartz for Appellant, John Earl Haskins, in pro. per., and Alfred Jay Luke for Respondents. THE COURT.

This appeal presents the same issues as those decided in Reed v. Norman, ante, p. 17 [256 P.2d 930] filed this day, and that decision is controlling herein.

The judgment is reversed.
